videos.headline: FSU's Francois intercepted after an underthrown pass
videos.description: Florida State QB Deondre Francois gets picked off by Syracuse's Christopher Fredrick after an underthrown pass.

videos.headline: FSU holds after Syracuse drives down field
videos.description: Florida State's defense stuffs Syracuse running back Dontae Strickland at the 1 yard line and limits the Orange to a field goal.

videos.headline: Syracuse Jamal Custis climbs the ladder for a 33-yd catch
videos.description: Syracuse backup QB Tommy DeVito sends one up for WR Jamal Custis and he pulls it down for a 33 yard reception.

videos.headline: Syracuse backup QB DeVito punches his way through for TD
videos.description: Syracuse backup quarterback Tommy DeVito plows through for an Orange TD.

videos.headline: Syracuse RB Howard breaks through for 45-yd run
videos.description: Orange RB Jarveon Howard breaks loose for a 45-yard gain to set up the touchdown to Ravian Pierce.

videos.headline: Francois does it all with 21-yd run and TD
videos.description: FSU QB Deondre Francois keeps it for a 21-yard run and then a 2-yard TD for the Seminoles first score.

videos.headline: Syracuse head coach gets hyped up after rare win vs. FSU
videos.description: Syracuse head coach Dino Babers gets fired up in the locker room after his Orange defeated the Seminoles.
